flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Discover Files\nlist_files ADR dir\nlist_files repo dir]

    B --> C{For each ADR}

    C --> D[Read ADR Rules\nread_file adr_path]
    D --> E[Read Code Files\nread_file each .cs file]
    E --> F[Analysis\nWrite Markdown analysis\nchecking each rule against code]

    F --> G{More ADRs?}
    G -- Yes --> C
    G -- No --> H[Reflection Step\nReview all analyses\nfor accuracy]

    H --> I[Re-read code files\nif needed for verification]
    I --> J[Compile and output\nfinal polished\nMarkdown report]

    J --> K[Print Console Report\nCOMPLIANT / NOT COMPLIANT\nper ADR with evidence]
    K --> L[Save compliance_report.md]
    L --> M([End])

    style A fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style M fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style H fill:#FF9800,color:#fff
    style F fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
